_:Neab748215ab04dc7af5cacdc9f55523e <http://schema.org/description> "The Criminal Procedure Rules govern the way criminal cases are managed, and set out the processes of the criminal courts. Criminal Procedure Rule Committee is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ." .
